Sofia Belattar (amụrụ na 9 Febụwarị na afọ 1995) bụ onye Moroccan judo.

N'afọ 2019, o ritere ihe nrite ọlaọcha na ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị 63 kilogram na African Judo Championships nke emere na Cape Town, South Africa. N'afọ 2020, o ritekwara ihe nrite ọlaọcha na ihe omume a na African Judo Championships nke emere na Antananarivo, Madagascar.
